# Fixture WIT deps are populated at build time from the shared
# p2-wit-deps/ and p3-wit-deps/ directories (see build.rs). Only the
# *contents* are ignored so that fixture-local custom packages can be
# re-included below ("it is not possible to re-include a file if a
# parent directory of that file is excluded").
*/wit/deps/*

# Fixtures with local-only WIT worlds manage their own deps
# (not populated from shared). Un-ignore so they stay committed.
!cron-service/wit/deps/*
!cron-component/wit/deps/*

# Custom cross-fixture package shared by the inter-component
# concurrency fixtures (not part of the shared wasi deps).
!*/wit/deps/wasmcloud-test-concurrent/

*-p3/wkg.lock
*-p3-*/wkg.lock

# Build artifacts
*/target/
target/
